items.title: Simon's problem - Wikipedia, the free encyclopedia
items.htmlTitle: Simon's problem - Wikipedia, the free encyclopedia
items.snippet:
This problem yields an oracle separation between BPP and BQP, unlike the 
separation provided by the Deutsch-Jozsa algorithm, which separates P and 
EQP.
